Package: sccore
Title: Core utilities for single-cell RNA-seq
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Peter", "Kharchenko", email = "peter_kharchenko@hms.harvard.edu", role = "aut"), person("Viktor","Petukhov", email="viktor.s.petuhov@ya.ru", role="aut"), person("Evan","Biederstedt", email="evan.biederstedt@gmail.com", role=c("cre", "aut")))
Description: Core utilities for single-cell RNA-seq data analysis. Contains functions for manipulating and plotting data via ggplot2.
